# =============================================================================
# WHAT IS INTENTIONALLY KEPT (not ignored)
# =============================================================================
# config.py            – no secrets, just constants (keep)
# requirements.txt     – keep so others can install deps
# main.py              – keep (core bot entry point)
# engine/              – keep (all logic)
# api/                 – keep
# scanner/             – keep
# ml/train_model.py    – keep the training script, not the trained model file
# ml_training_data.csv – keep (relatively small at 100 KB, useful for retraining)
# README*.md           – keep
# tests/               – keep

